customizations.markdownDescription:
```ts
customizations: {
  [partPath]: {
    visible: string,
    parentType: string,
    moveTo: string,
    primaryRenderType: RenderType,
    secondaryRenderType: RenderType
  }
}
```
***
Contains a list of key-value pairs where the keys are paths to model parts (minus the starting `models.`) and the values are the starting customizations for that part.
